==English==
===Pronunciation===
* [[IPA]] /saʃɪmɪ/

===Noun===
'''sashimi''' (''Collective Noun'')
# Slices of raw fish (and sometimes meat) (a Japanese dish widely available in Japanese, and sometimes Korean, restaurants and fast food outlets in English speaking countries).

When combined with rice is [[sushi]].

